The paper discusses the problem of interference in the downlink of multiple-antenna systems and proposes a new approach to exploit multiuser interference using symbol-level precoding. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), machine learning (cs.MM), and learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
